FBIS4-60866 "drsov084_s_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-084 Daily Report 2 May 1994 Georgia Shevardnadze: Russian Cooperation Needed To Form Army Shevardnadze: Russian Cooperation Needed To Form Army LD0205103794 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1000 GMT 2 May 94 LD0205103794 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Eduard Shevardnadze believes that a Georgian national army cannot be established without cooperation with Russia. In his traditional radio interview today he stressed that a new stage had begun in the formation of the Georgian army, connected with the appointment of a former general in the Russian Army Vardiko Nadibaidze to the post of Georgian minister of defense.
